name: NR Flexible Cell Shaping Low/Mid-Band
summary: This feature introduces an additional coverage shape.

parameters.name: CommonBeamforming.supportedCoverageOptions
parameters.description: This                                     attribute lists the supported coverage configuration                                     options.

parameters.name: CommonBeamforming.usedAzimuthCoverageWidth
parameters.description: This attribute shows the azimuth width in                                 use.

parameters.name: CommonBeamforming.usedElevationCoverageWidth
parameters.description: This attribute shows the elevation coverage width in                                 use.

parameters.name: CommonBeamforming.usedDigitalPan
parameters.description: This attribute shows the digital pan in                                 use.

activation_step: 1. Set the FeatureState.featureState attribute to ACTIVATED in the FeatureState=CXC4012756 MO instance.
deactivation_step: 1. Set the FeatureState.featureState attribute to DEACTIVATED in the FeatureState=CXC4012756 MO instance.
